# MCP server credentials for this repo's .mcp.json (GitHub + Trello).
# Copy this file to `.env.mcp` (gitignored), fill in your own values, then
# source it before starting Claude Code — see README's "MCP setup" section.
#
# NEVER commit a filled-in copy of this file. .mcp.json only ever contains
# ${VAR} placeholders; the actual secrets live here, locally, per-person.

# GitHub — a fine-grained PAT scoped to this repo (repo + workflow read/write
# as needed). Create at https://github.com/settings/tokens
GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN=

# Trello — API key + token from https://trello.com/power-ups/admin
# Board ID: open the board -> Show Menu -> ... -> More -> Print/Export ->
# the ID is in the exported URL, or call the Trello API's /members/me/boards.
TRELLO_API_KEY=
TRELLO_TOKEN=
TRELLO_BOARD_ID=
